Title: Is One Sentence A Paraphrase Of The Other?
Description: In this task we will check the quality of paraphrases (rewordings of a sentence which preserve meaning).
Keywords: meaning, semantic, similarity, text, paraphrase, style, grammatical
Input.text1: I won't miss any chance to send my love to you .
Input.text2: Not to my marriage will I omit A chance to let my love speak .
Answer.semantic-similarity.label: approximately the same meaning and the rewritten sentence is grammatical
